                  -}===-  Assassin Guild Help  -==={-
-------------------========] Help List One [========-----------------------
Command:         Cost:   Description:
COMBAT POWERS:
harm             50      Main spell attack. Simple but effective.
backstab                 Powerful first attack.  Make sure you are stealthy.

COMBAT AIDES:
o                        Toggle health monitor.
wimpydir <dir>           Set wimpy direction to dir.
wimpyhp <amt>            Set hit points at which you wimpy to amt.
cann					 Cannibalize corpse for healing.
consider <who>   15      Consider who's suitability for killing.
stalk <who>      15      Follow who around silently.
sneak <who>      75      Teleport silently to who.
escape			 15		 Teleport to guild hall.
reserve <what>   10      Reserve a monster so only you can attack it.
unreserve                Opposite of reserve.
